column14: MDP Ive proven plenty of times that Im not a psychic in terms of knowing the exact moment when something will happen I was way too early on my bet against this company this year but I didnt need any inside tips to see the blatant detachment from reality this companys leadership possesses They are driving this once respected brand straight into the ground They have no idea who the customer is or even what their product is They dont even know what year it is and it comes across in everything they say and do See you at the bottom
SPY Im calling super psych out head fake up is over and now it will be a slow inching downward for the rest of the day to kill premiums
Its a very smart move to cut out TV in my opinion If they really do pass local media group onto some sucker Im no longer a bear on MDP
